data.description: SELLER OFFERING UP TO $5000 TOWARDS BUYER'S CLOSING COSTS & PRE-PAIDS! Located in a tight nit community, this well maintained camelback home located in the heart of New Orleans is just 1 block from the historic Zulu parade route and just a few minutes from St. Charles Avenue's shops and eateries! Many of the home's original features have been well preserved: double french doors that mark the start of the home's hallway and transom windows lie above most interior and exterior doorways. The home also boasts both a front porch and side courtyard area along with storage sheds in the rear yard. You'll also find an optional 4th bedroom, office space, or sitting area at the top of the stairway leading to the second floor. Be one of the first to tour this spacious Central City gem!
